und-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\"\n        alt=\"Screenshot3\"\n        title=\"Screenshot3\"\n        data-src=\"/static/9055b6e471559b5ba3a0fcc30e342b33/a6d36/wa_screenshot_3.png\"\n        data-srcset=\"/static/9055b6e471559b5ba3a0fcc30e342b33/222b7/wa_screenshot_3.png 163w,\n/static/9055b6e471559b5ba3a0fcc30e342b33/ff46a/wa_screenshot_3.png 325w,\n/static/9055b6e471559b5ba3a0fcc30e342b33/a6d36/wa_screenshot_3.png 650w,\n/static/9055b6e471559b5ba3a0fcc30e342b33/27b8e/wa_screenshot_3.png 836w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1>Demo</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 1.0725rem\" > <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/PsA2EJ45YZc\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen style=\" position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \"></iframe> </div>\n<h1>Conclusion</h1>\n<p>Using the <code class=\"language-text\">whatsapp assistant</code> project, we can fire commands in Whatsapp, fetching information without even switching tabs, or opening browser. You have your assistant right in your whatsapp.\nHereby, we declare that the functionality implemented in this system was performed by understanding all the modules.</p>\n<h1>Limitation and Future Enhancements</h1>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> Remove ‘BOT’ group/user manual creation</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>View this project on <a href=\"https://github.com/o-x-y-g-e-n/whatsapp-assistant-bot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">github</a> 😺</p>\n</blockquote>","fields":{"slug":"research/product-design-and-health/"},"frontmatter":{"date":"06 December 2020","description":"Google Like assistant in whatsapp.","title":"Home Monitoring Solutions for children with Epilepsy","tags":["javascript, bot, whatsapp, automation"],"image":{"id":"d818b014-4dfc-588d-8157-7da36390873c","publicURL":"/static/969021026c1920ae61864b75ee84fa32/wa_header.jpg","childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5023474178403755,"src":"/static/969021026c1920ae61864b75ee84fa32/ce4b6/wa_header.jpg","srcSet":"/static/969021026c1920ae61864b75ee84fa32/1983d/wa_header.jpg 320w,\n/static/969021026c1920ae61864b75ee84fa32/994cc/wa_header.jpg 640w,\n/static/969021026c1920ae61864b75ee84fa32/ce4b6/wa_header.jpg 1280w,\n/static/969021026c1920ae61864b75ee84fa32/f01d2/wa_header.jpg 1920w,\n/static/969021026c1920ae61864b75ee84fa32/18d78/wa_header.jpg 2560w,\n/static/969021026c1920ae61864b75ee84fa32/aa2a3/wa_header.jpg 4272w","sizes":"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px"}}}},"timeToRead":8}},"pageContext":{"slug":"research/product-design-and-health/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"research/patient-and-family-centered-care/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"The Patient Centered Value System","date":"01 Dec, 2020"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2451431863","3039081124","469472723","63159454"]}